parameters:
Drillmaid: Geez, you've really... retrained yourself... In
such a short period... the atmosphere around you is
completely different...

Memimi: Drillmaid... I don't want to fight you. Where is
Mayor Orca Asparagus? I will defeat him and restore peace to
the city...

Drillmaid: Sorry, but I... I can't betray that person.
Overlooking a little girl is one thing... but to send a
monster like this... If you want to know where that person
is, you'll have to fight me.

Memimi: You're a tough one, Drillmaid... For a monster,
sticking to your convictions is the most important thing...
I understand your feelings, though.

Drillmaid: Come at me with all you've got... If you can't
defeat me, then dreaming of defeating Mayor Orca Asparagus
is just that, a dream! If you think you can save Mudgain
City, prove it!!!
Memimi: Cerberus Octopus... lend me your tentacles!
Memimi: Brachiocondor... thank you for your wings...

Drillmaid: GYAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHH!!! Impossible... With attack
power second only to Mayor Orca Asparagus, I... can't even
lift a finger...

Drillmaid: Understood... Go on, go ahead... Mayor Orca
Asparagus is at the Monster Fight Arena... in the place of
memories where our costume wrestling group's ring once
stood...

Memimi: Thank you, Drillmaid... I won't forget you... If
Mayor Shark Broccoli himself had gone down the path of
evil... surely, you and I would be like mirror images of
each other...

Drillmaid: Wait... gah, gahh... I understand... The only one
who can save that person is... now... only you can do it...
Take me with you too... please...
